In the theta band ( Figure 4 ), main effects of Training
[F(1,19)D19.83, p<0.001, !2D0.51] and Task [ F(1,19)D9.88,
p<0.01,!2D0.34] were observed, suggesting generally higher
theta ERS for trained compared to untrained problems (18.53
