of Training [ F(1,19)D9.25, p<0.01,!2D0.33], which was fur-
ther moderated by Task [ F(1,19)D6.67, p<0.05,!2D0.26]. A
higher alpha ERD was found in the untrained compared to the
trained problems (␀11.46 vs.␀2.74%), and the training effect
was stronger in the ﬁgural-spatial compared to the multiplica-
