left (compared) to right-hemispheric ERD, whereas the ﬁgural-
spatial problems were associated with stronger right than left-
hemispheric ERD [ F(1,19)D13.26, p<0.01,!2D0.41]. This was
also reﬂected in the interaction between Task, Hemisphere, and
