Discussion
To the best of our knowledge, this study represents the 
first exploration of functional interaction patterns using 
EEG during both RS and MA conditions in PD patients, 
comparing these patterns with those observed in HCs. 
Our investigation comprehensively assessed power spec -
tra and TGC in these contexts, facilitating direct compar -
isons within and between the PD patients and HCs. Theta 
