of Pearson’s correlation coefficients. Correlation (linear fit) between relative theta power in the RS condition at T5 and the HAMA scores in PD 
patients (n = 34, R2 linear = 0.737, p = 0.003). RS, resting‑state; HAMA, Hamilton Rating Scale for Anxiety; PD, panic disorder Page 11 of 16
