with the values being higher in HC than in SA patients. In the
gamma band, interhemispheric coherence was lower in P3-P4 in
HC. Alpha band interhemispheric coherence was not found to be
signiﬁcant. Coherence of the intra-hemispheric connections dif-
fered signiﬁcantly in the beta1 , beta2 and gamma bands. CoherenceTable 1
