Arithmetic Mental Task of EEG Signal Classification Using Statistical Modeling of The DWT Coefficient.pdf,2021,5,2,Arithmetic Mental Task of EEG Signal Classification Using Statistical Modeling of The DWT Coefficient.pdf,"Sk. Md. Ziad Rahman1, Israt Tawana1, H.M. Raihan Mostafiz1, Tanima Tasmin Chowdhury1,2, Celia Shahnaz2 
