III. METHODOLOGY  
 
 Our proposed methodology has five steps- A. Data 
Augmentation, B. Dominant Channel Selection, C. 
Selection of wavelet transform, D. Statistical model 
selection, E. Classifier selection. Fig 2 shows the block 
diagram of our methodology. 
 
 
