the data were collected with a sampling rate of 2048 Hz. The
beginning of each slide of the math presentations were markedwith a trigger into the EEG data, as well as the button presses
related to the instructions and the self-evaluation questions.
The triggers were sent wirelessly via Lab Streaming Layer (LSL;RRID:SCR 017631,
