There are a few limitations to discuss. First, common issue with
the phase synchrony method is volume conduction which means
that signal from two neighboring EEG electrodes is influencedby the same brain functions instead of separate brain functionsDownloaded from https://academic.oup.com/cercor/article/34/2/bhae025/7607164 by guest on 14 May 2025
