1A Machine Learning Approach in EEG -Based 
Assessment of Cognitive Load by Mental Arithmetic 
Tasks  
Phuc Khang Nguyen1,2, Quang Linh Huynh1,2* 
1 Department of Biomedical Engineering Physics, Faculty of Applied Science, Ho Chi Minh 
City University of Technology (HCMUT) , 268 Ly Thuong Kiet Street, District 10, Ho Chi 
