ORIGINAL ARTICLE
The neural differences of arithmetic verification performance 
depend on math skill: Evidence from event-related potential
Shiva  Taghizadeh1 |   Touraj Hashemi2 |   Ali Jahan3 |   Mohammad Ali Nazari1
