Arithmetic word problems describing discrete quantities: E.E.G evidence for
the construction of a situation model☆
Jeanne Bagnouda, Nicolas Burrab, Caroline Castelb, Jane Oakhillc, Catherine Thevenota,⁎
aUniversity of Lausanne, Institute of Psychology, CH-1015 Lausanne, Switzerland
bUniversity of Geneva, FPSE, Psychology Department, 40 bd du Pont D'Arve, CH-1205 Geneva, Switzerland
