Classification is a predictive modelling activity 
wherein a class label is predicted for a specific 
example of input data. It is a supervised learning 
technique that uses training data to determine or 
characterize the category of new set of observations. 
Classification is when a software learns from a dataset 
or observations and then categorizes subsequent 
