➄). For each channel,
grand average ERSPs were computed by averagingacross all 11 participants’ signiﬁcance-masked meanERSPs. Statistical reliability of grand averages wasassessed in a manner similar to that employed in theanalyses of individual participants. Time–frequencyand ERSP analyses can be accomplished by othermethods (e.g. continuous wavelet transform (CWT)
plots
20and Morlet wavelet transforms followed by
