Cortical source estimation . In practice, phase
coherence between the scalp-recorded EEG signals
was inﬂuenced by the volume conduction, which might
lead to spurious estimates on functional connectivity ofthe brain network ( Langer et al., 2012; Klados et al.,
2013 ). To address the problem, the EEG signals were
