Undirected graph construction . After computing the
PLV matrix with a size of 248 /C2248 from all the
pairwise nodes, an adjacency matrix ( ai,j) is obtained by
using one of the following two criteria: (1) a ﬁxedconnection density is set according to the Erdo ¨s–Re´nyi
model ( Erdo¨s and Re ´nyi, 1961 ) (i.e., p=2l n n/n, where
