tribution in the network; (2) a ﬁxed threshold is set for the
PLV matrices in the task period, which is the mean valueof the minimum PLVs in the resting-state adjacency matri-
ces with ﬁxed connection density from criterion (1), to ﬁnd
the between-groups diﬀerence in the reasoning-relatednetwork topology. After that, graph theory is applied to
the adjacency matrix to quantify the topological property
of the brain functional network.
