related to the computation, and we describe the potentialchange from the left side with three-dimensionally view-point in 200 ms. In this research, we focus on on-task inLevel 4 (both Type A and Type B), on-task in Level 6(Type B), oﬀ-task and memory-task. In comparisonbetween Type A and Type B in Level 4, we can ﬁnd somecommon patterns with respect to the positive potential, and
the same changes of the potential in the left temporal lobe
