III. SIMULATION RESULTS  
      The hybrid CNN -LSTM model's performance in MAT  
database classification is evaluated using acc, sen, spe, pre, 
F1_s, MCC and ka metrics.  The definitions and mathematical 
relations are derived  above . 
Accuracy:  It evaluates the ratio of instances that are correctly 
classified.  
