E. Brain Relaxation modeling 
Brain relaxation analysis is also performed with the value 
of PSD over time of alpha and beta bands after the completion 
of sustained mental tasks. The beta to alpha ratio (BAR) is obtained from the PSD analysis and taken as the brain relaxation factor. In this paper, BAR has been recorded over time and compared with the BAR of relax state. The graph is 
plotted with the BAR over different time interval and 
mathematical model is developed with least square algorithm in MATLAB platform which is reliable to fit the non- linear data. It is based on the calculation of the total square error as (4). 
