4. Methods
The model framework is shown in Figure 6. The first step was to preprocess the
raw EEG signals, and then extract the functional brain network construction and node
information composed of graph signals, respectively, which was followed by the use of the
SGATCNs classifier to identify different levels of cognitive workload. Sensors 2025 ,25, 2390 7 of 22
