4. Methods 
The model framework is shown in Figure 6. The ﬁrst step was to preprocess the raw 
EEG signals, and then extract the functional  brain network construction and node infor-
mation composed of graph signals, respecti vely, which was followed by the use of the 
SGATCNs classi ﬁer to identify di ﬀerent levels of cognitive workload. 
 
